Package org.forgerock.openidm.scheduler.impl

Class TaskScannerContext

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.scheduler.impl.TaskScannerContext
public class TaskScannerContext extends Object
Represents the information for a recurring TaskScannerJob. This is carried over across all instances of the TaskScannerJob
